1
00:00:29,620 --> 00:00:32,980
=The Secret of the Lost Pearl=

2
00:00:33,020 --> 00:00:34,940
=Episode 19=
(Fiction. Do not imitate.)

3
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:52,280
The signal range of this walkie-talkie

4
00:00:52,430 --> 00:00:53,750
won't exceed 50m

5
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:56,030
with the cave walls.

6
00:01:05,310 --> 00:01:06,150
Speak.

7
00:01:06,480 --> 00:01:07,400
So,

8
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:10,350
we're pretty close.

9
00:01:12,310 --> 00:01:13,400
Looking for me?

10
00:01:15,790 --> 00:01:17,480
Why use a walkie-talkie?

11
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:20,680
You have the stone box.

12
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:23,480
Tell me what you want.

13
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:26,280
Let's meet up.

14
00:01:26,790 --> 00:01:27,790
Without me,

15
00:01:28,040 --> 00:01:29,280
you can't get out of here.

16
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:31,520
Where's Chen Youxi?

17
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:33,640
Chen Youxi is with me.

18
00:01:34,230 --> 00:01:35,230
What if you

19
00:01:35,950 --> 00:01:37,680
wipe us out?

20
00:01:39,760 --> 00:01:40,950
You're overthinking.

21
00:01:42,070 --> 00:01:43,510
I just wanted to talk to you.

22
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:45,790
Talk?

23
00:01:46,590 --> 00:01:48,000
What's there to talk about with me?

24
00:01:48,040 --> 00:01:50,040
Are you scared?

25
00:01:51,070 --> 00:01:52,590
How can I trust you?

26
00:01:53,510 --> 00:01:54,710
It's come to this.

27
00:01:55,310 --> 00:01:56,710
Trust doesn't matter.

28
00:01:56,950 --> 00:01:58,480
We have to cooperate.

29
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:02,400
Continue.

30
00:02:04,430 --> 00:02:06,640
I need to tell you:

31
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:09,000
The main hall where the stone box

32
00:02:09,030 --> 00:02:09,870
was found was fake.

33
00:02:10,190 --> 00:02:11,190
Now,

34
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:13,310
we are in the real main hall.

35
00:02:14,030 --> 00:02:16,470
What did you say? I didn't hear.

36
00:02:16,470 --> 00:02:17,910
Repeat that.

37
00:02:25,750 --> 00:02:26,590
Bai Lingling,

38
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:28,200
speak.

39
00:02:51,870 --> 00:02:54,080
Huang, this is Li Ke's.

40
00:03:09,450 --> 00:03:10,320
Wow.

41
00:03:11,030 --> 00:03:12,630
This has to be the main hall.

42
00:03:13,030 --> 00:03:14,360
So much gold, silver, and jewels.

43
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:45,120
Don't move.

44
00:03:46,870 --> 00:03:47,710
Put down the gun.

45
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:48,800
Put it down.

46
00:03:58,310 --> 00:03:59,150
Chubby.

47
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:04,680
Unload the gun.

48
00:04:08,630 --> 00:04:09,910
Lu, over here.

49
00:04:10,030 --> 00:04:11,190
Amazing.

50
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,240
Here.

51
00:04:12,350 --> 00:04:13,190
Well done.

52
00:04:13,190 --> 00:04:14,080
He's untrustworthy.

53
00:04:17,430 --> 00:04:18,270
Bai Lingling,

54
00:04:19,130 --> 00:04:20,000
if the boss finds out

55
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,310
you joined Chen Youxi,

56
00:04:22,390 --> 00:04:23,600
guess what he would do?

57
00:04:23,750 --> 00:04:24,750
As for that,

58
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:27,160
you won't know anyway.

59
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:29,360
Don't waste words on them.
Get the rope.

60
00:04:29,510 --> 00:04:30,510
Tie them all up.

61
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:33,640
Don't move.

62
00:04:36,750 --> 00:04:37,590
Sit down.

63
00:04:38,510 --> 00:04:39,469
What are you looking at?

64
00:04:40,630 --> 00:04:41,480
And you.

65
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:43,520
Let's go.

66
00:04:44,390 --> 00:04:45,360
- Go.
- Move.

67
00:05:05,270 --> 00:05:06,110
Watch out!

68
00:05:11,310 --> 00:05:12,190
Huang Long!

69
00:05:26,430 --> 00:05:27,510
Stop running.

70
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:30,190
I can't breathe.

71
00:05:30,190 --> 00:05:31,920
You two, take the box to open the door.

72
00:05:31,950 --> 00:05:33,160
Hurry.

73
00:05:34,190 --> 00:05:35,030
Go.

74
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:09,920
The door is open.

75
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,270
Lu, quick.

76
00:06:19,750 --> 00:06:20,630
What now?

77
00:06:20,630 --> 00:06:21,950
We need to close the door.

78
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:34,320
Suppress them.

79
00:06:46,430 --> 00:06:47,270
Grenade!

80
00:07:33,630 --> 00:07:34,470
Where's the door?

81
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:39,560
Why is it silent?

82
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:41,270
Isn't silence a good thing?

83
00:07:41,430 --> 00:07:42,750
Do you want to hear from him?

84
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:44,290
Chen,

85
00:07:44,310 --> 00:07:46,070
if this place were open for visitors,

86
00:07:46,950 --> 00:07:48,560
would we get some profit share?

87
00:07:49,190 --> 00:07:51,630
It's not your tomb.
Why would you get a share?

88
00:07:51,870 --> 00:07:53,120
As long as we survive,

89
00:07:53,270 --> 00:07:54,510
I'll give you a bonus.

90
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:57,600
Chubby, remember what Lu said.

91
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:58,640
Wait.

92
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:00,160
You're bleeding.

93
00:08:00,630 --> 00:08:02,070
It's okay. My skin is thick.

94
00:08:02,830 --> 00:08:04,190
Did you get hurt while saving me?

95
00:08:06,430 --> 00:08:07,950
It hurts so much.

96
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:10,630
I can't take it. Wrap it for me.

97
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:13,080
Go there.

98
00:08:16,070 --> 00:08:17,160
Support me.

99
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:20,000
Sit down.

100
00:08:28,430 --> 00:08:29,270
Chen Youxi,

101
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:30,573
come and look at this.

102
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:33,840
Look at this.

103
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:36,480
Doesn't it look like the Mouth of Truth?

104
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:38,550
What? The Mouth of Truth?

105
00:08:40,550 --> 00:08:42,270
Don't look at me; I don't get it either.

106
00:08:42,870 --> 00:08:43,870
It means

107
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:45,670
if someone lies

108
00:08:45,749 --> 00:08:46,802
and puts their hand inside,

109
00:08:47,750 --> 00:08:48,720
it will bite them.

110
00:08:49,790 --> 00:08:50,630
Want to try?

111
00:08:50,910 --> 00:08:51,750
Try it.

112
00:08:51,870 --> 00:08:52,710
Me?

113
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:54,960
It'll surely bite off my hand.

114
00:08:55,870 --> 00:08:56,710
True.

115
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,040
What about you?

116
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:15,720
Your acting is so fake.

117
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:19,840
You're too old for this.

118
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:26,510
There's water. The water is flowing.

119
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:29,940
Tell me.

120
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:32,320
Why build a fountain

121
00:09:32,331 --> 00:09:33,517
inside this big manhole cover?

122
00:09:34,030 --> 00:09:34,870
A drinking source?

123
00:09:35,996 --> 00:09:37,242
This is called a hidden spring.

124
00:09:37,670 --> 00:09:39,120
What? What spring?

125
00:09:39,630 --> 00:09:40,910
A type of spring eye.

126
00:09:41,013 --> 00:09:42,320
The water flow stays this strong.

127
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:43,790
It won't overflow or decrease.

128
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:46,120
In Feng Shui,
it symbolizes stored abundance.

129
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,480
A place with a hidden spring

130
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:50,200
is most suitable for burying a woman.

131
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,360
If a hidden spring is found
inside a tomb,

132
00:09:52,510 --> 00:09:53,670
the tomb owner

133
00:09:53,670 --> 00:09:55,080
must be wealthy and noble

134
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:57,030
and must've been favored in life.

135
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:58,840
By your reasoning,

136
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:02,120
there's a 90% chance

137
00:10:02,550 --> 00:10:03,720
the tomb owner is a princess.

138
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:08,440
But which way leads to the main hall?

139
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:12,600
We've reached the end.

140
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,440
There's water everywhere ahead.

141
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:17,630
If we go further,
we'll have to turn back.

142
00:10:18,280 --> 00:10:19,746
Then we'll run into Huang Long again.

143
00:10:20,270 --> 00:10:21,150
Probably not.

144
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:22,600
Since we've made it here,

145
00:10:22,670 --> 00:10:23,670
there must be a way.

146
00:10:25,630 --> 00:10:27,000
Did I lose too much blood?

147
00:10:27,030 --> 00:10:28,600
Why do I feel anemic?

148
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:30,720
I feel dizzy.

149
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:36,720
I suddenly feel much better.

150
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:39,560
Lu,

151
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:40,680
look at this.

152
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:41,840
Any thoughts?

153
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:48,240
There's a big Bagua on top.

154
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:50,960
(Kun)
There's a pointer.

155
00:10:52,510 --> 00:10:53,960
This is the route.

156
00:10:54,750 --> 00:10:56,550
From my years of experience,
let me tell you.

157
00:10:57,790 --> 00:10:58,960
When this pointer aligns

158
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:00,550
(Kun)
with the character here,

159
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:03,270
the cover will open.

160
00:11:03,270 --> 00:11:05,510
We can go down from here and leave.

161
00:11:06,670 --> 00:11:08,720
But which direction

162
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:09,910
is the correct one?

163
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:11,910
If it's Bagua, ask Chen.

164
00:11:11,910 --> 00:11:12,870
He knows it well.

165
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:20,080
Xiu Gate.

166
00:11:20,650 --> 00:11:22,329
In the five elements,
it belongs to Water.

167
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:23,440
An auspicious gate.

168
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:26,480
It's located

169
00:11:29,150 --> 00:11:30,440
(Kan)
in the northern Kan.

170
00:11:31,030 --> 00:11:31,870
This one.

171
00:11:34,790 --> 00:11:35,630
Come on.

172
00:11:37,670 --> 00:11:38,750
It can't be that simple.

173
00:11:39,870 --> 00:11:41,320
Just turn it first.

174
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:43,120
If it doesn't work, we'll try another.

175
00:12:03,870 --> 00:12:04,720
What's happening?

176
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:06,100
Why is there so much water?

177
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:07,560
Hurry, this way.

178
00:12:11,390 --> 00:12:13,030
This side is spraying water too.

179
00:12:13,030 --> 00:12:14,790
Water's coming out above us too.

180
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:30,870
It's getting stronger.

181
00:12:31,550 --> 00:12:32,873
Lu, what's going on in there?

182
00:12:32,884 --> 00:12:34,149
- Careful!
- I'll turn it back.

183
00:12:34,160 --> 00:12:35,440
Turn it back!

184
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:37,870
- Turn it back!
- I can't turn it!

185
00:12:37,870 --> 00:12:38,710
Turn it!

186
00:12:42,910 --> 00:12:44,030
What's going on?

187
00:12:45,150 --> 00:12:46,080
Chen,

188
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:48,320
didn't you say this was the lucky gate?

189
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:50,440
How is this lucky?

190
00:12:50,550 --> 00:12:52,240
Chen, think of something!

191
00:12:52,390 --> 00:12:53,960
This won't work.

192
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:56,390
If the water keeps rising, we'll drown.

193
00:12:56,390 --> 00:12:58,440
Don't panic. There must be a way out.

194
00:12:58,790 --> 00:13:00,120
Lu, don't be afraid.

195
00:13:00,270 --> 00:13:01,390
I've got you.

196
00:13:01,390 --> 00:13:02,550
You're all talk.

197
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:03,870
If you're so capable,

198
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:05,000
block that thing.

199
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:07,120
I would've done it if I could.

200
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:13,870
Lu, hold this.

201
00:13:15,690 --> 00:13:16,550
Chubby,

202
00:13:16,550 --> 00:13:18,000
with this big jar,

203
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:19,600
I'll be grateful to you forever.

204
00:13:32,030 --> 00:13:32,870
How is it, Lu?

205
00:13:33,120 --> 00:13:34,670
Thanks to this big jar,

206
00:13:35,270 --> 00:13:37,200
or I'd be dead.

207
00:13:37,200 --> 00:13:38,440
Miss Bai, how are you?

208
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:40,150
I'm fine. Take care of yourselves.

209
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:43,510
Where is the exit?

210
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:45,200
I don't know.

211
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:47,030
The water will eventually drown us.

212
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:49,200
Hold on, Lu.

213
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:51,440
I'm holding on.

214
00:13:53,550 --> 00:13:54,440
Chubby,

215
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:56,750
this thing is leaking.

216
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:07,150
What do we do? The water keeps rising.

217
00:14:07,630 --> 00:14:08,603
It's already at the top.

218
00:14:09,550 --> 00:14:10,390
No.

219
00:14:10,683 --> 00:14:11,909
We're about to hit the ceiling.

220
00:14:13,840 --> 00:14:14,720
Look up, Lu.

221
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:31,630
Are we really going to die here?

222
00:14:42,480 --> 00:14:43,320
Chen Youxi.

223
00:14:43,790 --> 00:14:44,630
Chen.

224
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:14,160
(Bagua.)

225
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:17,790
(The manhole below is round,)

226
00:15:18,630 --> 00:15:20,000
(but the top is square.)

227
00:15:20,780 --> 00:15:23,559
(Ancient architecture emphasizes
a round heaven and a square earth.)

228
00:15:23,570 --> 00:15:25,446
(But here it's square heaven
and round earth.)

229
00:15:26,030 --> 00:15:26,870
(Could it be)

230
00:15:27,720 --> 00:15:29,200
(the layout here is upside down?)

231
00:15:32,790 --> 00:15:33,750
(If that's the case,)

232
00:15:35,150 --> 00:15:36,510
(the exit should be above.)

233
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:07,720
I found the exit. Follow me.

234
00:16:29,550 --> 00:16:31,120
Lu, are you okay?

235
00:16:33,870 --> 00:16:34,960
I'm fine.

236
00:16:41,080 --> 00:16:41,920
Chubby!

237
00:16:43,030 --> 00:16:43,870
Shutong!

238
00:16:48,630 --> 00:16:50,240
Fate isn't done with us yet.

239
00:16:54,030 --> 00:16:55,320
- Let's go.
- Go.

240
00:16:55,440 --> 00:16:56,280
That way.

241
00:17:14,570 --> 00:17:17,670
♪A tiny ark sails;
the sky opens its eyes♪

242
00:17:19,350 --> 00:17:23,030
♪Stillness in motion,
the earth plays its chord♪

243
00:17:24,090 --> 00:17:28,670
♪A leaf falls;
we cross through time and space♪

244
00:17:28,820 --> 00:17:35,820
♪In a blink, all things rest
upon our hands♪

245
00:17:36,380 --> 00:17:47,400
♪La la♪

246
00:17:54,150 --> 00:17:56,140
♪No line divides the border♪

247
00:17:56,580 --> 00:17:58,920
♪Nothing limits your performance♪

248
00:17:58,920 --> 00:18:01,290
♪Everything shows perfect harmony♪

249
00:18:01,290 --> 00:18:03,980
♪Love circles the sky,
the earth, and our faith♪

250
00:18:05,480 --> 00:18:07,190
♪Hey hey hey♪

251
00:18:08,520 --> 00:18:10,340
♪Hey hey hey♪

252
00:18:12,990 --> 00:18:13,990
♪Hey hey♪

253
00:18:14,140 --> 00:18:15,140
♪Hey hey♪

254
00:18:16,600 --> 00:18:17,680
♪Hey hey♪

255
00:18:19,310 --> 00:18:23,510
♪Step into the galaxy of colors♪

256
00:18:24,100 --> 00:18:27,810
♪Stars connect our hearts as one♪

257
00:18:30,090 --> 00:18:32,310
♪No difference between you and me♪

258
00:18:32,590 --> 00:18:34,920
♪No lead or side role on this stage♪

259
00:18:34,920 --> 00:18:37,130
♪A perfect life is something we share♪

260
00:18:37,350 --> 00:18:39,630
♪Love declares across the sky and earth♪

261
00:18:40,560 --> 00:18:45,350
♪Huo la yi ya, huo la yi ya♪

262
00:18:45,350 --> 00:18:50,200
♪Time and space go beyond all bounds♪

263
00:18:50,200 --> 00:18:55,050
♪Huo la yi ya, huo la yi ya♪

264
00:18:55,050 --> 00:18:57,140
♪This is our world♪

265
00:18:57,140 --> 00:19:02,170
♪Shining lives bring the change♪

266
00:19:06,700 --> 00:19:09,260
♪In a blink, to forever♪
